text: Georgiyevsky () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Yanybayevsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 3 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 111 km from Isyangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Georgiyevsky, Republic of Bashkortostan
